description:
A set of 20 emblems and 12 skins awarded as a bonus for purchasing the ACE COMBAT™ 7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Original Aircraft Series Set.

20 Bonus Emblems:
- 2 Nugget emblems commemorating the 25th anniversary of the ACE COMBAT series
- 5 emblems from squadrons in the game, including Ghost and Golem (Low-Vis)
- 13 emblems from other games in the series, including Nagase and Butterfly Master.

12 Bonus Skins:
- 12 skins from ACE COMBAT ZERO: THE BELKAN WAR, including F-15C Eagle Cipher Skin and Rafale M Espada Skin
name: ACE COMBAT™7: SKIES UNKNOWN - Original Aircraft Series Special Bonus Set
